  "Broker Comment" : "ON 4/29/2011, THE OFFICE OF FINANCIAL REGULATION ENTERED A FINAL ORDER ADOPTING THE STIPULATION AND CONSENT AGREEMENT IN THE MATTER OF ALLAN PHILLIP RECHT.  MR. RECHT NEITHER ADMITTED NOR DENIED THE FINDINGS BUT CONSENTED TO THE ENTRY OF FINDINGS BY THE OFFICE.  THE OFFICE FOUND THAT MR. RECHT ENGAGED IN INVESTMENT ADVISORY BUSINESS FROM OFFICES WITHIN THIS STATE WITHOUT THE BENEFIT OF LAWFUL REGISTRATION IN THE STATE OF FLORIDA PURSUANT TO SECTION 517.12(4), F.S.  MR. RECHT AGREED TO CEASE AND DESIST FROM ALL PRESENT AND FUTURE VIOLATIONS OF CHAPTER 517, F.S. AND THE ADMINISTRATIVE RULES THEREUNDER; AND TO PAY AN ADMINISTRATIVE FINE IN THE AMOUNT OF $10,000.  THE OFFICE AGREED TO APPROVE MR. RECHT'S APPLICATION AS AN ASSISTED PERSON (RA) WITH CAMARDA FINANCIAL ADVISORS, LLC, EFFECTIVE 4/29/2011.  MR. RECHT ENDED HIS AFFILIATION WITH CAMARDA FINANCIAL ADVISORS, LLC ON 9/2/2011 AND IS CURRENTLY AFFILIATED WITH CREATIVE PLANNING."
